HEADWORD: Entad
<hw>En"tad</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Ent-</ets> + L.
<ets>ad</ets> towards.]</ety> <fld>(Anat.)</fld> <def>Toward the inside
